pageContext.claim: “And in Ron's case, he's going against somebody that's got a lot of energy but he runs one of the worst, one of the biggest problem cities anywhere in the country. He's not doing the job.”
pageContext.analysis: It's not clear what Trump means by "biggest problem cities," but in a lot of ways, Tallahassee is average with assets and liabilities. But that's not the same as being one of the "worst."
